description: The mixture is composed of two glycopeptides which are comprised of either an F(6)A2 glycan or a F(3)A2 glycan attached to the asparagine amino acid of a peptide with the sequence Lysine-Valine-Alanine-Asparagine-Lysine-Threonine (KVANKT).This contains a mixture of F(3)A2-KVANKT and F(6)A2-KVANKT glycopeptides, ~ 6µg.m/z: 2104.9411
name: GPEP FA2 glycopeptide standard
